When the Market Price hits the Limit Order Price, the Limit Order (leg 1) will be executed and the Stop Market Order (leg 2) will be cancelled.
Conversely, if the Market Price hits the Stop Order Price first, then the Stop Market Order (leg 2) will be executed and the Limit Order (leg 1) will be cancelled.'.
